_1}\\times{\\mathbb\nT}^{e_1})$ iff $e_0\\le e_1$ and $c_0+e_0\\le c_1+e_1$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 10 Apr 2022 03:55:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 27 Sep 2022 09:56:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-28"}
