tFormer can serve as a good\nbaseline and aid future unified research for PPS. Our code and models are\navailable at https://github.com/lxtGH/Panoptic-PartFormer.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 10 Apr 2022 11:16:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 10 Jul 2022 09:30:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-12"}
